filedesc:
You can upload multiple files, each no larger than 300mb, to a total of 1GB.
Acceptable file formats: csv, doc, docx, jpg, jpeg, kml, ods, odt, pdf, png, ppt, pptx, rdf, rtf, txt, xls, xlsx, xml, zip
